cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

This paper focuses on indoor scene modeling using deep features from neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper involves reasoning about object relationships and global optimization, which are relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of convolutional networks and relation networks also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves modeling 3D geometry, which is relevant to computer graphics (cs.GR).
